#: kb/admin.py:2553
msgid ""
"Use the inline rows below to control progressive password/MFA lockouts. "
"Enter durations in seconds; the admin page also shows a readable "
"minutes/hours/days conversion. repeat_count=0 means the stage repeats "
"forever, which should normally be used on the final row."
